Global Pigment Yellow 191 Market Insights
Pigment Yellow 191 Market size was valued at USD 0.15 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.25 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Pigment Yellow 191 Market Overview
The Pigment Yellow 191 market has been experiencing significant growth due to increasing demand in various industries such as coatings, plastics, inks, and textiles. The market size in 2023 was valued at USD 1.2 billion and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2024 to 2031. The demand for environmentally friendly and high-performance pigments is driving market expansion, particularly in Asia-Pacific and Europe. The industry is also benefiting from continuous technological advancements in pigment production and the growing preference for durable and vibrant yellow pigments in industrial applications. The market's expansion is further supported by strong investments in R&D by key players, aimed at enhancing product efficiency and quality.

